snippet.title: Awakening Music
snippet.description:
Awakening Music is a pioneering and dynamic record label headquartered in London with offices in California and Cairo. Awakening introduced to the world global music sensations – the likes of Sami Yusuf, Maher Zain and Harris J. We produce faith inspired and values driven content. Our songs and music videos on Youtube and other digital platforms have been enjoyed by billions across the world.  
 
Awakening Music manages and represents Maher Zain (Sweden), Mesut Kurtis (Macedonia), Raef (USA), Harris J (UK) and Humood Alkhudher (Kuwait). Previously Sami Yusuf & Hamza Namira among others.
